data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4 bed, 2.5 bath offers a few upgrades throughout. This property boasts a second-story balcony and a covered back porch, providing the perfect spots to relax and enjoy nature. The large living room has a comfortable atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. You'll find the kitchen, complete with newer appliances, and ample storage space with a pantry. The nearby dining area is perfect for hosting dinners or gatherings. The 2nd level of this home is where you'll find the four bedrooms. The primary bedroom features a bathroom and direct access to the second-story balcony. The covered back porch offers a delightful space for outdoor living.
